      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ITA KEEPING (1) was quickly into stride and burnt early from out wide where she gave a sight, finishing second (17.23) and beaten a neck over 300m at this track. Must come into calculations. ZATARA MAC (8) had to overcome a collision with another runner and could manage only a distant sixth (17.65) in a Grade 6 over 300m at this track. Has the ability and can measure up. SWEETIE PIE (4) could manage only fourth after copping a check in the run last time in a Grade 6 at this track, finishing 2.5 lengths from the winner (17.59). Should be in this for a long way. LANSLEY WHISPER (6) was in the money last time at this track (17.35) in a Grade 6, finishing a 2 length third. Already a winner from this draw.",
